scenes.description: Kiara crouches down to interact with a KFP employee named Jimmy, praising him in their virtual restaurant.
Kiara watches Jimmy walk around the restaurant floor.
Kiara picks up Jimmy, showing him off to the camera while joking about him blinking.
Kiara summons a large swarm of KFP employees who fill the restaurant floor.
Kiara moves through the crowd of employees toward the service counter.
Kiara stands behind the counter, demonstrating the register and acting as a shopkeeper.
Kiara points out the menus and the kitchen area, suggesting they play a game.
Kiara walks to a preparation table with various food ingredients.
Kiara showcases a piece of fried chicken and the KFP bucket, interacting with her chat.
Kiara displays various burger ingredients laid out on the table.
Kiara takes a quick water break before starting the next segment.
